# Template CPPTRAJ script to clean up trajectories and prep them for KIF.
# Customizable params are "SYSTEM" and "OUT_PATH"
# Aim to have maybe 5000 to 10,0000 frames per system to analyse would be reasonable.
# You can control that via the last number in the trajin commands.

parm SYSTEM_apo.prmtop
trajin run_1/prod_md1.nc 1 last 1
trajin run_2/prod_md1.nc 1 last 1
trajin run_3/prod_md1.nc 1 last 1
trajin run_4/prod_md1.nc 1 last 1
trajin run_5/prod_md1.nc 1 last 1
strip :WAT,Na+,Cl- outprefix OUT_PATH/Trajectories/Stripped
autoimage
trajout OUT_PATH/SYSTEM_apo_all_runs.nc
run
clear all
exit
